author: John Dewey
message: Conflict is the gadfly of thought. It stirs us to observation and memory. It instigates to invention. It shocks us out of sheeplike passivity, and sets us at noting and contriving.
title: Thought of the day

author: Lao Tzu
message: He who conquers others is strong; He who conquers himself is mighty.
title: Thought of the day

author: Wayne Dyer
message: Anything you really want, you can attain, if you really go after it.
title: Thought of the day

author: John Dewey
message: Arriving at one point is the starting point to another.
title: Thought of the day
